{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "聖人為政一國，一國可倍也；", "text_normalized": "聖人為政一國，一國可倍也；", "canonical_ref": "19.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "大之為政天下，天下可倍也。", "text_normalized": "大之為政天下，天下可倍也。", "canonical_ref": "19.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "其倍之，非外取地也，因其國家去其無用之費，足以倍之。", "text_normalized": "其倍之，非外取地也，因其國家去其無用之費，足以倍之。", "canonical_ref": "19.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "聖王為政，其發令興事、使民用財也。", "text_normalized": "聖王為政，其發令興事、使民用財也。", "canonical_ref": "19.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "無不加用而為者，是故用財不費，民德不勞，其興利多矣。", "text_normalized": "無不加用而為者，是故用財不費，民德不勞，其興利多矣。", "canonical_ref": "19.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "其為衣裘何？", "text_normalized": "其為衣裘何？", "canonical_ref": "19.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "以為冬以圉寒，夏以圉暑。", "text_normalized": "以為冬以圉寒，夏以圉暑。", "canonical_ref": "19.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "凡為衣裳之道，冬加溫、夏加清者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "text_normalized": "凡為衣裳之道，冬加溫、夏加清者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "canonical_ref": "19.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "其為宮室何？", "text_normalized": "其為宮室何？", "canonical_ref": "19.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "以為冬以圉風寒，夏以圉暑雨。", "text_normalized": "以為冬以圉風寒，夏以圉暑雨。", "canonical_ref": "19.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "有盜賊加固者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "text_normalized": "有盜賊加固者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "canonical_ref": "19.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "其為甲盾五兵何？", "text_normalized": "其為甲盾五兵何？", "canonical_ref": "19.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "以為以圉寇亂盜賊，若有寇亂盜賊，有甲盾五兵者勝，無者不勝，是故聖人作為甲盾五兵。", "text_normalized": "以為以圉寇亂盜賊，若有寇亂盜賊，有甲盾五兵者勝，無者不勝，是故聖人作為甲盾五兵。", "canonical_ref": "19.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "凡為甲盾五兵，加輕以利堅而難折者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "text_normalized": "凡為甲盾五兵，加輕以利堅而難折者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "canonical_ref": "19.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "其為舟車何？", "text_normalized": "其為舟車何？", "canonical_ref": "19.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "以為車以行陵陸，舟以行川谷，以通四方之利。", "text_normalized": "以為車以行陵陸，舟以行川谷，以通四方之利。", "canonical_ref": "19.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "凡為舟車之道，加輕以利者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "text_normalized": "凡為舟車之道，加輕以利者，芊䱉不加者去之。", "canonical_ref": "19.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "凡其為此物也，無不加用而為者。", "text_normalized": "凡其為此物也，無不加用而為者。", "canonical_ref": "19.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "是故用財不費，民德不勞，其興利多矣。", "text_normalized": "是故用財不費，民德不勞，其興利多矣。", "canonical_ref": "19.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "有去大人之好聚珠玉、鳥獸、犬馬，以益衣裳、宮室、甲盾、五兵、舟車之數，於數倍乎？", "text_normalized": "有去大人之好聚珠玉、鳥獸、犬馬，以益衣裳、宮室、甲盾、五兵、舟車之數，於數倍乎？", "canonical_ref": "19.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "若則不難。", "text_normalized": "若則不難。", "canonical_ref": "19.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "故孰為難倍？", "text_normalized": "故孰為難倍？", "canonical_ref": "19.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "唯人為難倍。", "text_normalized": "唯人為難倍。", "canonical_ref": "19.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "然人有可倍也。", "text_normalized": "然人有可倍也。", "canonical_ref": "19.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "昔者聖王為法曰：", "text_normalized": "昔者聖王為法曰：", "canonical_ref": "19.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "「丈夫年二十，毋敢不處家。", "text_normalized": "「丈夫年二十，毋敢不處家。", "canonical_ref": "19.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "女子年十五，毋敢不事人。", "text_normalized": "女子年十五，毋敢不事人。", "canonical_ref": "19.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "」此聖王之法也。", "text_normalized": "」此聖王之法也。", "canonical_ref": "19.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "聖王既沒，於民次也。", "text_normalized": "聖王既沒，於民次也。", "canonical_ref": "19.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "其欲蚤處家者，有所二十年處家；", "text_normalized": "其欲蚤處家者，有所二十年處家；", "canonical_ref": "19.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "其欲晚處家者，有所四十年處家。", "text_normalized": "其欲晚處家者，有所四十年處家。", "canonical_ref": "19.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "以其蚤與其晚相踐，後聖王之法十年，若純三年而字，子生可以二三年矣。", "text_normalized": "以其蚤與其晚相踐，後聖王之法十年，若純三年而字，子生可以二三年矣。", "canonical_ref": "19.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "此不惟使民蚤處家而可以倍與？", "text_normalized": "此不惟使民蚤處家而可以倍與？", "canonical_ref": "19.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "且不然已。", "text_normalized": "且不然已。", "canonical_ref": "19.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "今天下為政者，其所以寡人之道多。", "text_normalized": "今天下為政者，其所以寡人之道多。", "canonical_ref": "19.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "其使民勞，其籍斂厚，民財不足，凍餓死者不可勝數也。", "text_normalized": "其使民勞，其籍斂厚，民財不足，凍餓死者不可勝數也。", "canonical_ref": "19.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "且大人惟毋興師以攻伐鄰國，久者終年，速者數月，男女久不相見，此所以寡人之道也。", "text_normalized": "且大人惟毋興師以攻伐鄰國，久者終年，速者數月，男女久不相見，此所以寡人之道也。", "canonical_ref": "19.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "與居處不安，飲食不時，作疾病死者，有與侵就伏橐、攻城野戰死者，不可勝數。", "text_normalized": "與居處不安，飲食不時，作疾病死者，有與侵就伏橐、攻城野戰死者，不可勝數。", "canonical_ref": "19.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "此不令為政者所以寡人之道數術而起與？", "text_normalized": "此不令為政者所以寡人之道數術而起與？", "canonical_ref": "19.39", "notes": ""}
