{"segment_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i", "source_id": "mozi-019-economy-of-expenditures-i__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "不聖人為政、其所以眾人之道亦數術而起與？", "text_normalized": "不聖人為政、其所以眾人之道亦數術而起與？", "canonical_ref": "19.41", "notes": ""}
